Situated on a beautiful estate in Somerset West, Spanish Farm Guest Lodge (a 2020 Hotels Combined Recognition of Excellence Award winner) offers luxury guesthouse bedrooms and self-catering villas, all set within lush indigenous gardens boasting views of False Bay and the surrounding mountains. With private nature pools and wooden decks, each villa also has a wood burning fireplace to keep winter chills at bay. Even better is that you will get 15 percent off the listed winter rates from June 1 to August  31, 2021. When booking, please email info@spanishfarm.co.za and quote the promo code -SFGLWIN21. Subject to availability. T’s & C’s apply. For more information on the Cape Summer Villas Boutique Collection, see capesummervillas.co.za. 